OL,3,CMan sentenced to two years for series
OL,4,Cof assaults on emergency staff
OL,6,FA Jersey man who has been sentenced to
OL,7,Ftwo years in prison for a series of
OL,8,Fassaults said he wasn't intoxicated
OL,9,Fand added "I'm a little bit of a d***".
OL,11,FGlen Rhys Le Claire, 32, appeared in
OL,12,FJersey's Royal Court on Friday 3
OL,13,FJanuary 2025.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to one charge of
OL,16,Flarceny and five counts of assault
OL,17,Fcommitted over a period between mid-
OL,18,FMay and early August this year.
OL,20,FAll six charges took place when Le
OL,21,FClaire was intoxicated.
