OL,3,CMan sentenced to two years for series
OL,4,Cof assaults on emergency staff
OL,6,FSome later offences were committed
OL,7,Fwhile Le Claire was already under
OL,8,Finvestigation and on bail for earlier
OL,9,Fcrimes.
OL,11,FOne of the assaults was against a
OL,12,Fparamedic, and another was against a
OL,13,Fpolice officer carrying out their duty.
OL,15,FRobin Smith, Chief of Police said:
OL,16,F"Assaulting emergency workers whilst
OL,17,Fcarrying out their duties on behalf of
OL,18,FIslanders is a serious offence.
OL,20,F"This sentence should serve as a clear
OL,21,Fdeterrent."
